<lb n="6" break="no"/>rvīṣvakhamuci mucukuṁdā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>śramē rājyamuccaiḥ staḷyāṁ
<lb n="8"/>prābhānavaḷyā(ṁ)malabhata
<lb n="9"/>khilanādurgamākramya samya
<lb n="10" break="no"/>k <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> tadvaṁṣamauktikamaṇēḥ
