<lb n="21" break="no"/>śvarābaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">3</supplied> tasmin Īśvara
<lb n="22" break="no"/>vatsarē himakratau pauṣē
<lb n="23"/>ca māsē tithau paṁcamyāṁ
<lb n="24"/>budhavāsa<unclear>rē</unclear> śatabhiṣajyukṣē ca
<lb n="25"/>pakṣē sitē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ratnāravyā dhava
<lb n="26" break="no"/>ḷācaḷasya nikaṭē sā haivagaṁgā
<lb n="27" break="no"/>taṭē kānhōjikṣitipāḷakasya
